Comment:
 This file transcribes struct layouts from the Linux kernel UAPI headers
 (arch/x86/include/uapi/asm/sigcontext.h and
 include/uapi/asm-generic/ucontext.h) and inherits their licence. The
 Linux-syscall-note exception is what permits userspace to use these
 definitions, so it imposes no obligation on code that merely uses sigctx.

